    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113510/extras/bac5811c75d6023a904759f2bef4bf97.poster.avif?t=1766131517\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113510/extras/bac5811c75d6023a904759f2bef4bf97.webm?t=1766131517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113510/extras/bac5811c75d6023a904759f2bef4bf97.mp4?t=1766131517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Skidaddle Skidoodle是一款单人街机游戏，你扮演一个小侏儒法师，努力保护森林及其居民免受破坏自然和谐的邪恶生物的侵害。 使用各种法术来击败入侵者，并将温暖和平静的日子带回森林。 控制敌人的数量，在这个神奇的领域恢复自然力量的平衡。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113510/extras/c5a43de8a91b19b350237950e15901a7.poster.avif?t=1766131517\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113510/extras/c5a43de8a91b19b350237950e15901a7.webm?t=1766131517\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113510/extras/c5a43de8a91b19b350237950e15901a7.mp4?t=1766131517\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>主要特点：</strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>身临其境的单人游戏体验：与不同的敌人和具有挑战性的水平进行惊险刺激的单人任务。<br></li><li>丰富的法术库：掌握广泛的魔法咒语，以战略性地击败各种敌人。<br></li><li>迷人的主角：踏入一个可爱的侏儒法师的鞋子，致力于保卫森林。<br></li><li>迷人的视觉和声音：享受一个精心制作的世界与惊人的图形和迷人的配乐。<br></li><li>动态自然平衡：通过管理敌人种群并将平衡带回魔法森林来恢复和谐。</li></ul>",
